  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/816490/extras/1fb30683c7ad93317c637b48640b88ad.poster.avif?t=1767462759\" width=564 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/816490/extras/1fb30683c7ad93317c637b48640b88ad.webm?t=1767462759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/816490/extras/1fb30683c7ad93317c637b48640b88ad.mp4?t=1767462759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's winter and cats are still outside. Cold and alone. Find them and bring them home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features 12+ charming winter landscapes with over 120 little cats to find. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free Christmas Update adds 4 festive isles. Is there a cat in a gift box? And then another Christmas Update adds 2 more magical places.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open cars and boxes, rummage through piles of wood, search the forests. Cats are well hidden but they meow when you get near so listen closely and you might just be able to find them all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/816490/extras/f68b7d1250fef219cd80938c44de0d21.poster.avif?t=1767462759\" width=702 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/816490/extras/f68b7d1250fef219cd80938c44de0d21.webm?t=1767462759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/816490/extras/f68b7d1250fef219cd80938c44de0d21.mp4?t=1767462759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/816490/extras/1fb30683c7ad93317c637b48640b88ad.poster.avif?t=1767462759\" width=564 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/816490/extras/1fb30683c7ad93317c637b48640b88ad.webm?t=1767462759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/816490/extras/1fb30683c7ad93317c637b48640b88ad.mp4?t=1767462759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's winter and cats are still outside. Cold and alone. Find them and bring them home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features 12+ charming winter landscapes with over 120 little cats to find. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free Christmas Update adds 4 festive isles. Is there a cat in a gift box? And then another Christmas Update adds 2 more magical places.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open cars and boxes, rummage through piles of wood, search the forests. Cats are well hidden but they meow when you get near so listen closely and you might just be able to find them all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/816490/extras/f68b7d1250fef219cd80938c44de0d21.poster.avif?t=1767462759\" width=702 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/816490/extras/f68b7d1250fef219cd80938c44de0d21.webm?t=1767462759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/816490/extras/f68b7d1250fef219cd80938c44de0d21.mp4?t=1767462759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
